-- 2010-09-21T14:52:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/smi-stock-benchmark-declines-sgs-syngenta-lonza-slide-richemont-gains.html
Swiss stocks declined, as losses by
SGS SA and Syngenta AG offset gains by ABB Ltd. and Cie.
Financiere Richemont SA.  The benchmark Swiss Market Index dropped 0.3 percent to
6,440.56 at 4:51 p.m. in Zurich, after swinging between gains
and losses at least 14 times.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Hadfield at 
